metadata.description: Your NFT Access for 2 to the AM Festival NFT table section. Cirque Noir welcomes you to join us April 1-3 for a truly magical weekend as we introduce you to our first boutique festival experience in Austin, TX. From sunset to sunrise, each day you will be teleported to a place of wonder. A place of creativity, where every sense will be activated. We’ll follow the frequencies of the globe’s greatest purveyors of sound to curate a transformative moment in time. This is a 21+ event.
